### Healthcheck (no auth)
GET {{url}}/auth/healthcheck

### Seed data (no auth)
POST {{url}}/populate

### Login as seeded USER and store JWT
POST {{url}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "alice@carebridge.io",
  "password": "password123"
}

> {%
  client.global.set("jwt_token", response.body.token);
%}

### Read all chat rooms (requires USER/ADMIN)
GET {{url}}/chatrooms
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

### Read messages for a seeded room (replace chatRoomId if needed)
GET {{url}}/messages?chatRoomId=1
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

### Create message
POST {{url}}/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 2,
  "chatRoomId": 1,
  "message": "Hello World!"
}


